      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "YESZEM (3) improving filly who comes here with a distinct fitness edge over most of these from a good gate. Came out fast from the wide gate and stuck on well to secure sixth over 1400m at Parkes. Has options from the gate and no excuses today. HEARD OF HIM (5) began awkwardly on debut and never gave up when fourth over 1200m at Bathurst. Open to further improvement and should appreciate the extra trip. YES ARNIE (10) gripped on late in the heavy conditions with a respectable fourth over 1412m at Taree on the quick back-up. Well drawn and capable of taking this out. JONSON (1) starting to put it together this time in and a win looks imminent. Speared across from the wide gate and held on well to run third over 1400m at Newcastle. Drawn out again and not to be underestimated.",
